In Season versus Off Season Activity by Teams¶

  • Mean of In Season = 14.657143
  • Mean of Off Season = 32.971429
In [381]:
dfSeason = pd.DataFrame()
dfOffSeason = pd.DataFrame()
for i in range(2001, 2018,1):
    mask = (df.index > '7-%s' % str(i-1)) & (df.index <= '2-27-%s' % str(i))
    dfSeason = dfSeason.append(df[mask])
    
    mask2 = (df.index >= '2-27-%s' % str(i-1)) & (df.index < '7-%s' % str(i))
    dfOffSeason = dfOffSeason.append(df[mask2])
    
print(dfSeason.info(), dfOffSeason.info())
